^C02 LEVEL 9 - Beta Labs 4

^C01 Briefing:
^C04 Seems like the Beta Labs Sector 3 had a lot problems with their self-contained 
power supply and security systems. Our guess is that this part of the lab complex 
wasn't ready for the dangerous experiments they conducted there. Now listen up! The 
Beta Labs Sector 4 was concerned with testing a cyborg where even the human components 
were artificially produced. You'd better keep your eyes open. This kind of experiment 
can't be good if it succeeds, even only partly.

