^C02 GENERAL INFORMATION ABOUT THIS AREA

^C04 The Beta Labs Sector 4 does research on cyborgs and weapons. There are several 
sections concentrating on different aspects of the experiments. This area contains 
prison cell blocks, storage areas and labs. It also connects the Beta Labs with the 
Communications Area.

